- Yes, we can.

647
00:52:42,460 --> 00:52:43,664
Together we can.

648
00:52:43,797 --> 00:52:45,831
You can't give up on us.

649
00:52:45,898 --> 00:52:48,501
Julie, you're all I've got.

650
00:52:48,601 --> 00:52:50,670
And I don't ever
want to live without you.

651
00:52:50,771 --> 00:52:53,206
Ever.

652
