Hey, there they are.

653
00:52:56,175 --> 00:52:57,376
Come on.

654
00:52:57,543 --> 00:52:58,411
Oh, shit.

655
00:52:58,579 --> 00:53:01,581
You fucking bitch,
your ass is grass.

656
00:53:01,715 --> 00:53:02,882
What do they want?

657
00:53:03,016 --> 00:53:06,286
Whatever it is,
it sure ain't good.

658
00:53:06,420 --> 00:53:09,623
