I feel so stiff.

696
00:55:28,295 --> 00:55:29,429
Come on.

697
00:55:49,547 --> 00:55:50,650
Come on.

698
00:56:04,130 --> 00:56:05,297
Shut the door.

699
00:56:15,141 --> 00:56:17,610
