a nice place on the water.

774
01:01:00,994 --> 01:01:03,030
I'm gonna get a gig in a band.

775
01:01:03,130 --> 01:01:05,599
And you can hang out all night
and party, and watch me play.

776
01:01:12,606 --> 01:01:14,942
